<text layer="eta" matrix="1 0 0 1 -1.87936 -73.6396" transformations="translations" pos="32 224" stroke="black" type="minipage" width="672" height="30.9384" depth="19.008" valign="top" size="small">\textbf{Observation.} Suppose $x \ne y$. Then $A_{x,y} = 1$ if and only if Quicksort compares $x$ and $y$, with $x$ being the pivot at that time.</text>
<text layer="theta" matrix="1 0 0 1 -1.87936 -137.64" transformations="translations" pos="32 224" stroke="black" type="minipage" width="672" height="20.1528" depth="8.208" valign="top" size="small">\textbf{Observation.} Quicksort makes 
$\sum_{x} \sum_{y \ne x} A_{x,y}$ comparisons.</text>
</page>
