<text layer="alpha" transformations="translations" pos="32 496" stroke="black" type="minipage" width="672" height="19.3928" depth="5.404" valign="top" style="center">The Expected Number of Comparisons of Quicksort</text>
<text layer="beta" transformations="translations" pos="32 416" stroke="black" type="label" width="331.69" height="16.6224" depth="4.632" valign="baseline" size="small">Shuffle the input array randomly!</text>
<text layer="gamma" transformations="translations" pos="32 368" stroke="black" type="label" width="493.306" height="27.4872" depth="15.552" valign="baseline" size="small" style="math">\mathbf{E}[ \textnormal{number of comparisons}] = \mathbf{E}\left[
\sum_{x} \sum_{y \ne x} A_{x,y} \right]</text>
<text layer="delta" transformations="translations" pos="304 320" stroke="black" type="label" width="210.034" height="17.9208" depth="10.44" valign="baseline" size="small" style="math"> = \sum_x \sum_{y \ne x} \mathbf{E}[A_{x,y}]</text>
<text layer="epsilon" matrix="1 0 0 1 -240 -16" transformations="translations" pos="352 240" stroke="red" type="label" width="586.08" height="16.6224" depth="4.632" valign="baseline" size="small">Probability that $x$ is an ancestor of $y$ in the Quicksort tree</text>
