<text layer="alpha" matrix="1 0 0 1 -16 96" transformations="translations" pos="48 384" stroke="black" type="label" width="190.926" height="23.5648" depth="14.504" valign="baseline" style="math">\mathbf{E}[A_{x,y}] = \frac{1}{ |[x:y]|}</text>
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 0 64" transformations="translations" pos="32 384" stroke="black" type="minipage" width="672" height="36.0948" depth="22.176" valign="top">For simplicity, suppose the input elements are $1,2, \dots, n$, randomly shuffled.</text>
<text layer="beta" matrix="1 0 0 1 -16 -48" transformations="translations" pos="48 384" stroke="black" type="label" width="178.102" height="23.5648" depth="14.504" valign="baseline" style="math">\mathbf{E}[A_{i,j}] = \frac{1}{ |[i:j]|}</text>
<text layer="gamma" matrix="1 0 0 1 176 -48" transformations="translations" pos="48 384" stroke="black" type="label" width="121.069" height="23.5648" depth="14.504" valign="baseline">$ = \frac{1}{|i-j|+1}$.</text>
<text layer="delta" transformations="translations" pos="32 272" stroke="black" type="label" width="271.393" height="23.5816" depth="9.604" valign="baseline">\textbf{Example.} $\mathbf{E}[A_{3,5}] = \frac{1}{3} $</text>
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 128 -48" transformations="translations" pos="32 272" stroke="black" type="label" width="142.764" height="23.5816" depth="9.604" valign="baseline" style="math">\mathbf{E}[A_{8,7}] = \frac{1}{2} </text>
<text layer="epsilon" matrix="1 0 0 1 0 -192" transformations="translations" pos="32 368" stroke="black" type="label" width="464.952" height="17.9208" depth="10.44" valign="baseline" size="small" style="math">\mathbf{E}[ \textnormal{number of comparisons}] = \sum_i \sum_{j \ne i} \mathbf{E} [A_{i,j}]</text>
<text layer="zeta" matrix="1 0 0 1 464 -192" transformations="translations" pos="32 368" stroke="black" type="label" width="195.058" height="20.1984" depth="12.432" valign="baseline" size="small" style="math"> = \sum_{i} \sum_{j \ne i} 
\frac{1}{|i-j|+1}</text>
<text layer="eta" matrix="1 0 0 1 16 -16" transformations="translations" pos="272 96" stroke="red" type="label" width="309.838" height="17.9352" depth="5.976" valign="baseline" size="small">Evaluate this sum (Homework)</text>
<path stroke="red" arrow="normal/normal">
432 112 m
448 128
496 128
544 144
576 160 c
</path>
<text layer="theta" matrix="1 0 0 1 16 -48" transformations="translations" pos="272 96" stroke="red" type="label" width="221.237" height="16.6224" depth="4.632" valign="baseline" size="small">I&apos;m doing it here now.</text>
</page>
