<text matrix="1 0 0 1 -21.1217 16.2329" transformations="translations" pos="32 368" stroke="blue" type="label" width="239.899" height="23.1" depth="11.496" valign="baseline" size="small" style="math"> = 2 \cdot \sum_{i=1}^n \sum_{j=1}^{i-1 }
\frac{1}{i-j+1} </text>
